msgid "Sturmpanzer_II_descr"
msgstr ""
"Developed in 1941 and based on the Pz.Kpfw. II Ausf. B. All manufactured "
"vehicles were sent to the front and lost. The SPGs were used by the Afrika "
"Division in Libya and Tunisia."

